 if the memory\nis wisely taken under control, or cancelled by shuffling the data. All this\nmakes compelling the conclusion that $\\mu = 2.138 \\pm 0.01$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Aug 2001 15:36:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
